    AsynchronousMessageParser

    Parser for the Asynchronous Message of the iSCSI Protocol (RFC3720).

    Volker Wildi

      • getAsyncVCode

        public final byte getAsyncVCode()
        Returns the code of the iSCSI Asynchronous message.

        AsyncVCode is a vendor specific detail code that is only valid if the AsyncEvent field indicates a vendor specific event. Otherwise, it is reserved.

        Returns:
        The Asynchronous vendor code.
        See Also:
        AsynchronousMessageParser.AsyncEventCodes
